  }, "Note (10/18/2020): In the discussion below, some readers mentioned that I did not fully understand the IKE protocol or IPsec. I believe that I understand the protocol fundamentals well enough. Still, I haven\u2019t been professionally in the networking industry for a few years. I admit that some of the things I mention here may be outdated or incorrect. However, I still insist that IPsec is an overly complex protocol. Thanks to the readers for corrections.")), mdx("p", null, "What I like about IPsec is that the ESP payload can be directly packed after an IP portion of a packet. It\u2019s because the ESP is registered as one of the ", mdx("a", _extends({
